            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"bluebikes-after-dark-and-the-lit-street-grid\">Bluebikes after dark and the lit street grid</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Lens:</strong> compare <em>night</em> trip ends (9pm\u20136am) to <em>day</em> ends using distance to the <strong>nearest streetlight</strong> among ~74k city fixtures.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Data:</strong> Bluebikes Feb\u2013Apr 2026 trip files, Boston streetlight locations, hospital locations (coordinate sanity check), and the BTD traffic <em>study catalog</em> CSV.</span></span>"
